Title: Kang18_8vs8
Description: Droplet-based scRNA-seq PBMC data from 8 Lupus patients before and after 6h-treatment with INF-beta. Represented as a SingleCellExperiment; derived from GEO accession number GSE96583.

Title: Crowell19_4vs4
Description: Single-nuclei RNA-seq data of 8 CD-1 male mice (age 11 weeks) split into 2 groups with 4 animals each: vehicle and peripherally lipopolysaccharaide (LPS) treated mice; derive from Figshare DOI:10.6084/m9.figshare.8976473.v1.
